[[File:Intencity Logo.png|right]]
'''Intencity''' is a chain of video arcades owned by Australian company [[Village Roadshow Limited]], with arcade locations in most states of Australia. The chain was originally launched in 1995 as part of a venture called ''Village Nine Leisure'' (a partnership between Village, [[Nine Network]] and [[Westfield Group]]).

